room_title: Escape room "CXI" by AmeriEscape Room in Las Vegas
room_address: 210 E Charleston Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89104
room_description: Today your laboratory is being presented with a once in a lifetime opportunity. The FBI has contacted you with a long-term contract, but you’ll have to prove that you’re up to the task. Your test mission is all lab work. You have only one hour to complete it. If you’re successful, your company will not only receive the lucrative contract, but the fame and recognition that comes with earning such a prestigious job. The clock is ticking! You can do it!
